To comment in notebook cell:

Summary Table:


| Action                | Vim Keys                  | Command Palette        |
|-----------------------|---------------------------|------------------------|
| Comment lines         | Shift+V, select, :s/^/# / | "Toggle Line Comment"  |
| Uncomment lines       | Shift+V, select, :s/^# // | "Toggle Line Comment"  |
| Comment whole cell    | ggVG, :s/^/# /            | "Toggle Line Comment"  |

Thelast one works after ggVG do Ctrl+ /
